Aaron Rodgers’ reworked deal now is signed, per sources. Here are the “on paper” concessions in the new contract:

🏈2023 year is voided.

🏈Forfeiture provisions were removed from the contract, preventing the Packers from pursuing prorated portions of Rodgers’ signing bonus.

node.text: The Cowboys said the results of Dak Prescott's MRI showed a muscle strain in his right shoulder, according to ESPN’s Todd Archer. Prescott will undergo treatment and evaluated on a day-to-day basis. No word on when he will practice again, but Archer reported that Prescott has a latissimus strain.
Some of the moments from Aaron Rodgers' unfiltered air-it-out day...

" Aaron Rodgers on discussions with the Packers organization'.
